{"tid":208190,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人訓係到個陣個肚會發出「咕～咕」既聲？","createTime":"2017-04-19T11:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T13:26:42.000Z","uid":8895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"146c2490ed13f738bb4c7265a641bbbac9b1ad77","tid":208190,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我訓係到個陣會發出咕咕咕既聲<br />\n唔係肚餓 又唔係胃唔舒服 但唔知點解總係發生聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同朋友去旅行個訓陣會有啲尷尬 唔知以為肚餓 但實際唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2792ec426ef64a12f0cabb7d806a03a3b2deda","tid":208190,"uid":2321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解我訓係到個陣會發出咕咕咕既聲<br />\n唔係肚餓 又唔係胃唔舒服 但唔知點解總係發生聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同朋友去旅行個訓陣會有啲尷尬 唔知以為肚餓 但實際唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時會，但比較少出現"},{"pid":"6fdb7f318d6ef706e0f6d816f7bb9f0da97f4500","tid":208190,"uid":98494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"消化中"},{"pid":"9f6d71fcde42b1fa1b214f04a85f308a8db007a4","tid":208190,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解我訓係到個陣會發出咕咕咕既聲<br />\n唔係肚餓 又唔係胃唔舒服 但唔知點解總係發生聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同朋友去旅行個訓陣會有啲尷尬 唔知以為肚餓 但實際唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時會，但比較少出現</blockquote><br />\n成日都會咕 企同坐都無事 一訓就咕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好尷尬"},{"pid":"1ddb925820db19b469d9e236e459a924b130c9b3","tid":208190,"uid":8895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消化中</blockquote><br />\n唔覺老豆同哥咕 朋友都聽唔到 但自己有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正常人都應